snippet.title: ARTISTdirect
snippet.description:
Since 1996, ARTISTdirect has been all about the music - direct from the ARTIST.

Get daily music news, interviews and premieres via https://www.ARTISTdirect.com

Watch exclusive interviews and live performances from our video vault here on the ARTISTdirect YouTube Channel including appearances from Charli XCX, James Bay, Iron & Wine, Hollywood Undead, Slash, KoRn and Travis Barker.
